msgid "An astute professorial type strokes his goatee as he studies a painting. You recognize him as Caldwell Phillips, the dean of Miskatonic University."
msgstr "Un professore dall'aria perspicace si accarezza il pizzetto mentre studia un dipinto. Si tratta di Caldwell Phillips, il rettore della Miskatonic University."

